==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tippler
<hw>Tip"pler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
keeps a tippling-house.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Latimer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who habitually indulges in the excessive use of
spirituous liquors, whether he becomes intoxicated or not.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tippling-house</ent>⟦br⟧
